equations () can be written as [F_A^cl  ,_i^cl ]=0  ,    i=1,2  .
 This implies that the field strength
definition 
for an on-shell gauge field corresponds (up to an irrelevant shift
by the constant curvature ) to a Heisenberg Lie algebra in
